original_title: Keighley & Worth Valley Railway – 2019 Diesel & Mixed Traction Gala
overview: Featuring footage from every day at the gala, which was held from the 3rd May to the 6th May, this 2 DVD set features 13 locomotives in action throughout the 4 days
